<p>Hello {{user.firstName}},</p>

<p>A milestone in your project has been updated:</p>

<div class="summary">
  <h3><span class="status-badge" style="background-color: {{statusColor}};">{{status}}</span> {{milestone.title}}</h3>
  <p><strong>Project:</strong> {{project.title}}</p>
  <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{milestone.description}}</p>
  <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{formatCurrency (divide milestone.amount 100)}}</p>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{formatDate (date)}}</p>
  {{#if message}}
  <p><strong>Message:</strong> {{message}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p>You can view the full project details in your dashboard.</p>

<p><a href="{{dashboardLink}}" class="button">View Project</a></p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The {{siteName}} Team</p>